  "comment": "The Helix XP is a powerful 150W LED gobo flower which produces an array of multi-coloured rotating gobos. All 8 gobos are interchangeable along with a separate colour wheel featuring 9 colours plus open. To further enhance this effect, an additional 11-piece gobo pack is also included to cover many popular events and celebrations. Clever programming allows users to select a single gobo and then have specific colours from the colour wheel added to them manually whilst being activated automatically or via sound. The unit, although compact in size, has a wide beam angle but still packs a punch over a long distance thanks to its superior optics and high output LED. The Helix XP can be linked with the Helix Scan XP and Helix Roller XP to create synchronised shows.\n\nVersions:\n1.000 Release version, based on an original by Artoodk\n",
